#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:134
msgid "Style subtitle"
msgstr "Določitev sloga podnaslova"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:141
msgid ""
"This is a global, simple subtitle styling possibility. It only allows one "
"style for all subtitles of the project. Accessible through the \"T drop\" "
"icon in the subtitle edit widget."
msgstr ""
"To je globalna, preprosta možnost oblikovanja podnaslovov. Omogoča le en "
"slog za vse podnaslove projekta. Dostopno prek ikone »T drop« v gradiniku za "
"urejanje podnaslovov."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:145
msgid ""
"**SRT** supports markup for: bold, italic, underline, text color and line "
"break."
msgstr ""
"**SRT** podpira označevanje za: krepko, ležeče, podčrtano, barvo besedila in "
"prelom vrstice."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:147
msgid "``<b>text in boldface</b>``"
msgstr "»<b>besedilo v krepki pisavi</b>«"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:148
msgid "``<i>text in italics</i>``"
msgstr "»<i>besedilo v ležeči pisavi</i>«"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:149
msgid "``<u>text underlined</u>``"
msgstr "»<u>podčrtano besedilo</u>«"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:150
msgid ""
"``<font color=\"#00ff00\"> text in green</font>`` you can use the font tag "
"only to change color."
msgstr ""
"»<font color=\"#00ff00\"> besedilo v zeleni</font>« - oznako pisave lahko "
"uporabite tudi samo za spreminjanje barve."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:151
msgid ""
"And all combined: ``<font color=\"#00ff00\"><b><i><u>All combined</u></i></"
"b></font>``"
msgstr ""
"In vse skupaj: »<font color=\"#00ff00\"><b><i><u>Vse skupaj</u></i></b></"
"font>«"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:152
msgid ""
"**Line break:** Add on the end of each line a ``<br>`` (for break). Now the :"
"file:`.srt` file is stored correct and reopened with the line break. The "
"subtitle in the subtitle window will be all in 1 line after several save but "
"the breaks is working."
msgstr ""
"**Prelom vrstice:** na koncu vsake vrstice dodajte »<br>« (za prelom). Zdaj "
"je datoteka :file:`.srt` shranjena pravilno in ponovno odprta z prelomom "
"vrstice. Podnaslov v oknu podnaslovov bo cel v eni vrstici po več "
"shranjevanjih, vendar prelom deluje."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:154
msgid ":kbd:`Alt+Arrow` jumps from subtitle to subtitle."
msgstr ":kbd:`Izmenjalka+smerna tipka` skoči s podnaslova na podnaslov."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:158
msgid "Import and export subtitle"
msgstr "Uvoz in izvoz podnaslovov"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:162
msgid "Allows importing .vtt (Web Video Text Tracks) and .sbv (YouTube) files."
msgstr "Omogoča uvoz datotek .vtt (Web Video Text Tracks) in .sbv (YouTube)."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:164
msgid ""
"Importing **SRT**, **ASS**, **VTT** and **SBV** subtitle file: :"
"menuselection:`Menu --> Project --> Subtitles --> Import Subtitle File`"
msgstr ""
"Uvažanje datoteke podnaslovov **SRT**, **ASS**, *VTT* in *SBV*: :"
"menuselection:`Meni --> Projekt --> Podnaslovi --> Uvozi datoteko "
"podnaslovov`"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:166
msgid ""
"Exporting **SRT** subtitles only: :menuselection:`Menu --> Project --> "
"Subtitles --> Export Subtitle File`"
msgstr ""
"Samo izvažanje podnaslovov **SRT**: :menuselection:`Meni --> Projekt --> "
"Podnaslovi --> Izvozi datoteko podnaslovov`"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:174
msgid ""
"Allow overriding of detected codecs through a list of available codecs, and "
"show a preview to make choice easier."
msgstr ""
"Dovolite preglasitev zaznanih kodekov prek seznama razpoložljivih kodekov in "
"pokažite predogled, da boste lažje izbrali."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:178
msgid "Spelling check"
msgstr "Preverjanje črkovanja"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/subtitles.rst:182
msgid ""
"Spelling check for subtitle is integrated and shows incorrect words by a red "
"wiggly line. Right-click on the word and you get a list of possible words "
"you can then choose by clicking on it."
msgstr ""
"Preverjanje črkovanja podnaslova je integrirano in prikazuje napačne besede "
"z rdečo vijugavo črto. Z desno tipko miške kliknite besedo in odpre se "
"seznam možnih nadomestnih besed, ki jih lahko izberete s klikom nanje."
